      <title>摩根士丹利目标投资 10 亿美元用于能源转型</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/morgan-stanley-targets-1-billion-for-energy-transition-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，摩根士丹利资产管理部门计划筹集至少 10 亿美元资金，成立一支专门投资能源转型的新基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/morgan-stanley-targets-1-billion-for-energy-transition-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 16:52:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>开云集团发出 Gucci 警告，市值蒸发 68 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/kering-shares-drop-after-warning-of-plunge-in-gucci-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国奢侈品集团开云集团警告称，由于其傲慢的外观失去了中国消费者的青睐，其古驰品牌第一季度销售额下降了约 20%，此后该公司股价暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/kering-shares-drop-after-warning-of-plunge-in-gucci-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 08:19:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着美联储降息，债券收益率下跌：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储维持 2024 年三次降息的预测后，股市上涨，债券收益率下跌，缓解了人们对推迟扭转一代人以来最大幅度加息的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 21:49:47 GMT</pubDate>
